for ext in addrtype cluster connbytes connlimit connmark cpu dccp dscp ecn esp hashlimit helper iprange ipvs layer7 length mark osf owner physdev pkttype policy quota rateest realm recent sctp set socket statistic string tcpmss time tos ttl u32 unclean; do f="./libxt_$ext.man"; cf="./libxt_$ext.c"; if [ -f "$f" ] && grep -Eq "NFPROTO_IPV4|NFPROTO_UNSPEC" "$cf"; then echo -e "\t+ $f" >&2; echo ".SS $ext"; cat "$f"; continue; fi; f="./libipt_$ext.man"; if [ -f "$f" ]; then echo -e "\t+ $f" >&2; echo ".SS $ext"; cat "$f"; continue; fi; done >matches4.man;

. /home/sargon/workspace/gluon/openwrt/include/shell.sh; (cd /home/sargon/workspace/gluon/openwrt/build_dir/linux-ar71xx_generic/packages/ipkg-ar71xx/kmod-ipv6/CONTROL;  )
ipkg-build -c -o 0 -g 0 /home/sargon/workspace/gluon/openwrt/build_dir/linux-ar71xx_generic/packages/ipkg-ar71xx/kmod-ipv6 /home/sargon/workspace/gluon/openwrt/bin/ar71xx/packages

mkdir -p /home/sargon/workspace/gluon/openwrt/bin/ar71xx/packages /home/sargon/workspace/gluon/openwrt/build_dir/linux-ar71xx_generic/packages/ipkg-ar71xx/kmod-ip6tables/CONTROL /home/sargon/workspace/gluon/openwrt/staging_dir/target-mips_r2_uClibc-0.9.33.2/pkginfo
. /home/sargon/workspace/gluon/openwrt/include/shell.sh; export modules=; add_module() { priority="$1"; mods="$2"; boot="$3"; shift 3; for mod in $mods; do if [ -e /home/sargon/workspace/gluon/openwrt/build_dir/linux-ar71xx_generic/packages/ipkg-ar71xx/kmod-ip6tables/lib/modules/3.3.8/$mod.ko ]; then mkdir -p /home/sargon/workspace/gluon/openwrt/build_dir/linux-ar71xx_generic/packages/ipkg-ar71xx/kmod-ip6tables/etc/modules.d; echo "$mod" >> /home/sargon/workspace/gluon/openwrt/build_dir/linux-ar71xx_generic/packages/ipkg-ar71xx/kmod-ip6tables/etc/modules.d/$priority-ip6tables; fi; done; if [ -e /home/sargon/workspace/gluon/openwrt/build_dir/linux-ar71xx_generic/packages/ipkg-ar71xx/kmod-ip6tables/etc/modules.d/$priority-ip6tables ]; then if [ "$boot" = "1" ]; then mkdir -p /home/sargon/workspace/gluon/openwrt/build_dir/linux-ar71xx_generic/packages/ipkg-ar71xx/kmod-ip6tables/etc/modules-boot.d; ln -s ../modules.d/$priority-ip6tables /home/sargon/workspace/gluon/openwrt/build_dir/linux-ar71xx_generic/packages/ipkg-ar71xx/kmod-ip6tables/etc/modules-boot.d/; fi; modules="${modules:+$modules }$priority-ip6tables"; fi; }; add_module "49" "nf_defrag_ipv6 nf_conntrack_ipv6 ip6_tables ip6table_filter ip6table_mangle ip6_queue ip6table_raw ip6t_ah ip6t_eui64 ip6t_frag ip6t_ipv6header ip6t_mh ip6t_hbh ip6t_rt ip6t_LOG ip6t_REJECT" ""; if [ -n "$modules" ]; then mkdir -p /home/sargon/workspace/gluon/openwrt/build_dir/linux-ar71xx_generic/packages/ipkg-ar71xx/kmod-ip6tables/etc/modules.d; mkdir -p /home/sargon/workspace/gluon/openwrt/build_dir/linux-ar71xx_generic/packages/ipkg-ar71xx/kmod-ip6tables/CONTROL; echo "#!/bin/sh" > /home/sargon/workspace/gluon/openwrt/build_dir/linux-ar71xx_generic/packages/ipkg-ar71xx/kmod-ip6tables/CONTROL/postinst; echo "[ -z \"\$IPKG_INSTROOT\" ] || exit 0" >> /home/sargon/workspace/gluon/openwrt/build_dir/linux-ar71xx_generic/packages/ipkg-ar71xx/kmod-ip6tables/CONTROL/postinst; echo ". /etc/functions.sh" >> /home/sargon/workspace/gluon/openwrt/build_dir/linux-ar71xx_generic/packages/ipkg-ar71xx/kmod-ip6tables/CONTROL/postinst; echo "load_modules $modules" >> /home/sargon/workspace/gluon/openwrt/build_dir/linux-ar71xx_generic/packages/ipkg-ar71xx/kmod-ip6tables/CONTROL/postinst; chmod 0755 /home/sargon/workspace/gluon/openwrt/build_dir/linux-ar71xx_generic/packages/ipkg-ar71xx/kmod-ip6tables/CONTROL/postinst; fi

( echo "Package: kmod-usb-ohci"; echo "Version: 3.3.8-1"; DEPENDS='kernel (=3.3.8-1-d6597ebf6203328d3519ea3c3371a493)'; for depend in kmod-usb-core; do DEPENDS=${DEPENDS:+$DEPENDS, }${depend##+}; done; echo "Depends: $DEPENDS"; echo "Provides: "; echo "Source: package/kernel"; echo "Section: kernel"; echo "Status: unknown hold not-installed"; echo "Essential: no"; echo "Priority: optional"; echo "Maintainer: OpenWrt Developers Team <openwrt-devel@openwrt.org>"; echo "Architecture: ar71xx"; echo "Installed-Size: 0"; echo -n "Description: "; . /home/sargon/workspace/gluon/openwrt/include/shell.sh; getvar V_Package_kmod_usb_ohci_description | sed -e 's,^[[:space:]]*, ,g'; ) > /home/sargon/workspace/gluon/openwrt/build_dir/linux-ar71xx_generic/packages/ipkg-ar71xx/kmod-usb-ohci/CONTROL/control

. /home/sargon/workspace/gluon/openwrt/include/shell.sh; export modules=; add_module() { priority="$1"; mods="$2"; boot="$3"; shift 3; for mod in $mods; do if [ -e /home/sargon/workspace/gluon/openwrt/staging_dir/target-mips_r2_uClibc-0.9.33.2/root-ar71xx/tmp-kmod-usb-ohci/lib/modules/3.3.8/$mod.ko ]; then mkdir -p /home/sargon/workspace/gluon/openwrt/staging_dir/target-mips_r2_uClibc-0.9.33.2/root-ar71xx/tmp-kmod-usb-ohci/etc/modules.d; echo "$mod" >> /home/sargon/workspace/gluon/openwrt/staging_dir/target-mips_r2_uClibc-0.9.33.2/root-ar71xx/tmp-kmod-usb-ohci/etc/modules.d/$priority-usb-ohci; fi; done; if [ -e /home/sargon/workspace/gluon/openwrt/staging_dir/target-mips_r2_uClibc-0.9.33.2/root-ar71xx/tmp-kmod-usb-ohci/etc/modules.d/$priority-usb-ohci ]; then if [ "$boot" = "1" ]; then mkdir -p /home/sargon/workspace/gluon/openwrt/staging_dir/target-mips_r2_uClibc-0.9.33.2/root-ar71xx/tmp-kmod-usb-ohci/etc/modules-boot.d; fi; }; add_module "50" "ohci-hcd" "1"; if [ -n "$modules" ]; then mkdir -p /home/sargon/workspace/gluon/openwrt/staging_dir/target-mips_r2_uClibc-0.9.33.2/root-ar71xx/tmp-kmod-usb-ohci/etc/modules.d; fi; done; if [ -e /home/sargon/workspace/gluon/openwrt/staging_dir/target-mips_r2_uClibc-0.9.33.2/root-ar71xx/tmp-kmod-mac80211/etc/modules.d/$priority-mac80211 ]; then if [ "$boot" = "1" ]; then mkdir -p /home/sargon/workspace/gluon/openwrt/staging_dir/target-mips_r2_uClibc-0.9.33.2/root-ar71xx/tmp-kmod-mac80211/etc/modules-boot.d; fi; }; add_module "21" "mac80211" ""; if [ -n "$modules" ]; then mkdir -p /home/sargon/workspace/gluon/openwrt/staging_dir/target-mips_r2_uClibc-0.9.33.2/root-ar71xx/tmp-kmod-mac80211/etc/modules.d; mkdir -p /home/sargon/workspace/gluon/openwrt/staging_dir/target-mips_r2_uClibc-0.9.33.2/root-ar71xx/tmp-kmod-mac80211/CONTROL; touch /home/sargon/workspace/gluon/build/ar71xx-generic/kernel/lzma-loader/.prepared
make -C /home/sargon/workspace/gluon/build/ar71xx-generic/kernel/lzma-loader CROSS_COMPILE="mips-openwrt-linux-uclibc-" \
	LZMA_TEXT_START=0x80a00000 \
	LOADER_DATA= \
	FLASH_OFFS=0x52000 \
	FLASH_MAX=0 \
	BOARD="mzk-w300nh" \
	clean all
make[5]: Entering directory '/home/sargon/workspace/gluon/build/ar71xx-generic/kernel/lzma-loader'
rm -f loader *.elf *.bin *.o

mips-openwrt-linux-uclibc-gcc -D__KERNEL__ -Wall -Wstrict-prototypes -Wno-trigraphs -Os -fno-strict-aliasing -fno-common -fomit-frame-pointer -G 0 -mno-abicalls -fno-pic -ffunction-sections -pipe -mlong-calls -fno-common -ffreestanding -fhonour-copts -mabi=32 -march=mips32r2 -Wa,-32 -Wa,-march=mips32r2 -Wa,-mips32r2 -Wa,--trap -D_LZMA_PROB32 -DCONFIG_KERNEL_CMDLINE='"board=MZK-W300NH console=ttyS0,115200 mtdparts=spi0.0:256k(u-boot)ro,64k(u-boot-env)ro,960k(kernel),6784k(rootfs),128k(art)ro,7744k@0x50000(firmware)"' -DCONFIG_FLASH_OFFS=0x52000 -DCONFIG_FLASH_MAX=0 -DCONFIG_BOARD_MZK_W300NH -c -o board.o board.c
mips-openwrt-linux-uclibc-gcc -D__KERNEL__ -Wall -Wstrict-prototypes -Wno-trigraphs -Os -fno-strict-aliasing -fno-common -fomit-frame-pointer -G 0 -mno-abicalls -fno-pic -ffunction-sections -pipe -mlong-calls -fno-common -ffreestanding -fhonour-copts -mabi=32 -march=mips32r2 -Wa,-32 -Wa,-march=mips32r2 -Wa,-mips32r2 -Wa,--trap -D_LZMA_PROB32 -DCONFIG_KERNEL_CMDLINE='"board=MZK-W300NH console=ttyS0,115200 mtdparts=spi0.0:256k(u-boot)ro,64k(u-boot-env)ro,960k(kernel),6784k(rootfs),128k(art)ro,7744k@0x50000(firmware)"' -DCONFIG_FLASH_OFFS=0x52000 -DCONFIG_FLASH_MAX=0 -DCONFIG_BOARD_MZK_W300NH -c -o printf.o printf.c
mips-openwrt-linux-uclibc-gcc -D__KERNEL__ -Wall -Wstrict-prototypes -Wno-trigraphs -Os -fno-strict-aliasing -fno-common -fomit-frame-pointer -G 0 -mno-abicalls -fno-pic -ffunction-sections -pipe -mlong-calls -fno-common -ffreestanding -fhonour-copts -mabi=32 -march=mips32r2 -Wa,-32 -Wa,-march=mips32r2 -Wa,-mips32r2 -Wa,--trap -D_LZMA_PROB32 -DCONFIG_KERNEL_CMDLINE='"board=MZK-W300NH console=ttyS0,115200 mtdparts=spi0.0:256k(u-boot)ro,64k(u-boot-env)ro,960k(kernel),6784k(rootfs),128k(art)ro,7744k@0x50000(firmware)"' -DCONFIG_FLASH_OFFS=0x52000 -DCONFIG_FLASH_MAX=0 -DCONFIG_BOARD_MZK_W300NH -c -o LzmaDecode.o LzmaDecode.c
mips-openwrt-linux-uclibc-ld -static --gc-sections -no-warn-mismatch -e startup -T loader.lds -Ttext 0x80a00000 -o loader head.o loader.o cache.o board.o printf.o LzmaDecode.o
mips-openwrt-linux-uclibc-objcopy -O binary -R .reginfo -R .note -R .comment -R .mdebug -S loader loader.bin
mips-openwrt-linux-uclibc-ld -r -b binary --oformat elf32-tradbigmips -o loader2.o loader.bin
mips-openwrt-linux-uclibc-ld -e startup -T loader2.lds -Ttext 0x80060000 -o loader.elf loader2.o

mips-openwrt-linux-uclibc-gcc -D__KERNEL__ -Wall -Wstrict-prototypes -Wno-trigraphs -Os -fno-strict-aliasing -fno-common -fomit-frame-pointer -G 0 -mno-abicalls -fno-pic -ffunction-sections -pipe -mlong-calls -fno-common -ffreestanding -fhonour-copts -mabi=32 -march=mips32r2 -Wa,-32 -Wa,-march=mips32r2 -Wa,-mips32r2 -Wa,--trap -D_LZMA_PROB32 -DCONFIG_KERNEL_CMDLINE='"board=TL-MR3420 console=ttyS0,115200"' -DCONFIG_FLASH_OFFS=0x22000 -DCONFIG_FLASH_MAX=0 -DCONFIG_BOARD_TL_MR3420_V1 -c -o LzmaDecode.o LzmaDecode.c
mips-openwrt-linux-uclibc-ld -static --gc-sections -no-warn-mismatch -e startup -T loader.lds -Ttext 0x80a00000 -o loader head.o loader.o cache.o board.o printf.o LzmaDecode.o
mips-openwrt-linux-uclibc-objcopy -O binary -R .reginfo -R .note -R .comment -R .mdebug -S loader loader.bin
mips-openwrt-linux-uclibc-ld -r -b binary --oformat elf32-tradbigmips -o loader2.o loader.bin
mips-openwrt-linux-uclibc-ld -e startup -T loader2.lds -Ttext 0x80060000 -o loader.elf loader2.o

mips-openwrt-linux-uclibc-ld -static --gc-sections -no-warn-mismatch -e startup -T loader.lds -Ttext 0x80a00000 -o loader head.o loader.o cache.o board.o printf.o LzmaDecode.o
mips-openwrt-linux-uclibc-objcopy -O binary -R .reginfo -R .note -R .comment -R .mdebug -S loader loader.bin
mips-openwrt-linux-uclibc-ld -r -b binary --oformat elf32-tradbigmips -o loader2.o loader.bin
mips-openwrt-linux-uclibc-ld -e startup -T loader2.lds -Ttext 0x80060000 -o loader.elf loader2.o

mips-openwrt-linux-uclibc-gcc -D__KERNEL__ -Wall -Wstrict-prototypes -Wno-trigraphs -Os -fno-strict-aliasing -fno-common -fomit-frame-pointer -G 0 -mno-abicalls -fno-pic -ffunction-sections -pipe -mlong-calls -fno-common -ffreestanding -fhonour-copts -mabi=32 -march=mips32r2 -Wa,-32 -Wa,-march=mips32r2 -Wa,-mips32r2 -Wa,--trap -D_LZMA_PROB32 -DCONFIG_KERNEL_CMDLINE='"board=TL-WR741ND console=ttyS0,115200"' -DCONFIG_FLASH_OFFS=0x22000 -DCONFIG_FLASH_MAX=0 -DCONFIG_BOARD_TL_WR741ND_V1 -D__ASSEMBLY__ -c -o head.o head.S

mips-openwrt-linux-uclibc-gcc -D__KERNEL__ -Wall -Wstrict-prototypes -Wno-trigraphs -Os -fno-strict-aliasing -fno-common -fomit-frame-pointer -G 0 -mno-abicalls -fno-pic -ffunction-sections -pipe -mlong-calls -fno-common -ffreestanding -fhonour-copts -mabi=32 -march=mips32r2 -Wa,-32 -Wa,-march=mips32r2 -Wa,-mips32r2 -Wa,--trap -D_LZMA_PROB32 -DCONFIG_KERNEL_CMDLINE='"board=TL-WR741ND console=ttyS0,115200"' -DCONFIG_FLASH_OFFS=0x22000 -DCONFIG_FLASH_MAX=0 -DCONFIG_BOARD_TL_WR741ND_V1 -c -o printf.o printf.c
mips-openwrt-linux-uclibc-gcc -D__KERNEL__ -Wall -Wstrict-prototypes -Wno-trigraphs -Os -fno-strict-aliasing -fno-common -fomit-frame-pointer -G 0 -mno-abicalls -fno-pic -ffunction-sections -pipe -mlong-calls -fno-common -ffreestanding -fhonour-copts -mabi=32 -march=mips32r2 -Wa,-32 -Wa,-march=mips32r2 -Wa,-mips32r2 -Wa,--trap -D_LZMA_PROB32 -DCONFIG_KERNEL_CMDLINE='"board=TL-WR741ND console=ttyS0,115200"' -DCONFIG_FLASH_OFFS=0x22000 -DCONFIG_FLASH_MAX=0 -DCONFIG_BOARD_TL_WR741ND_V1 -c -o LzmaDecode.o LzmaDecode.c
mips-openwrt-linux-uclibc-ld -static --gc-sections -no-warn-mismatch -e startup -T loader.lds -Ttext 0x80a00000 -o loader head.o loader.o cache.o board.o printf.o LzmaDecode.o
mips-openwrt-linux-uclibc-objcopy -O binary -R .reginfo -R .note -R .comment -R .mdebug -S loader loader.bin
mips-openwrt-linux-uclibc-ld -r -b binary --oformat elf32-tradbigmips -o loader2.o loader.bin
mips-openwrt-linux-uclibc-ld -e startup -T loader2.lds -Ttext 0x80060000 -o loader.elf loader2.o

make[4]: Leaving directory '/home/sargon/workspace/gluon/openwrt/target/linux/ar71xx/image/lzma-loader'

make V=ss -C lzma-loader KDIR=/home/sargon/workspace/gluon/build/ar71xx-generic/kernel LOADER=loader-tl-wr741nd-v2.gz KERNEL_CMDLINE="board=TL-WR741ND console=ttyS0,115200" LZMA_TEXT_START=0x80a00000 LOADADDR=0x80060000 BOARD="tl-wr741nd-v2" FLASH_OFFS=0x22000 FLASH_MAX=0 compile loader.gz
make[4]: Entering directory '/home/sargon/workspace/gluon/openwrt/target/linux/ar71xx/image/lzma-loader'
mkdir /home/sargon/workspace/gluon/build/ar71xx-generic/kernel/lzma-loader
cp -fpR ./src/* /home/sargon/workspace/gluon/build/ar71xx-generic/kernel/lzma-loader/
touch /home/sargon/workspace/gluon/build/ar71xx-generic/kernel/lzma-loader/.prepared
make -C /home/sargon/workspace/gluon/build/ar71xx-generic/kernel/lzma-loader CROSS_COMPILE="mips-openwrt-linux-uclibc-" \
	LZMA_TEXT_START=0x80a00000 \
	LOADER_DATA= \
	FLASH_OFFS=0x22000 \
	FLASH_MAX=0 \
	BOARD="tl-wr741nd-v2" \
	clean all

mips-openwrt-linux-uclibc-gcc -D__KERNEL__ -Wall -Wstrict-prototypes -Wno-trigraphs -Os -fno-strict-aliasing -fno-common -fomit-frame-pointer -G 0 -mno-abicalls -fno-pic -ffunction-sections -pipe -mlong-calls -fno-common -ffreestanding -fhonour-copts -mabi=32 -march=mips32r2 -Wa,-32 -Wa,-march=mips32r2 -Wa,-mips32r2 -Wa,--trap -D_LZMA_PROB32 -DCONFIG_KERNEL_CMDLINE='"board=TL-WR941ND console=ttyS0,115200"' -DCONFIG_FLASH_OFFS=0x22000 -DCONFIG_FLASH_MAX=0 -DCONFIG_BOARD_TL_WR841ND_V3 -c -o LzmaDecode.o LzmaDecode.c
mips-openwrt-linux-uclibc-ld -static --gc-sections -no-warn-mismatch -e startup -T loader.lds -Ttext 0x80a00000 -o loader head.o loader.o cache.o board.o printf.o LzmaDecode.o
mips-openwrt-linux-uclibc-objcopy -O binary -R .reginfo -R .note -R .comment -R .mdebug -S loader loader.bin
mips-openwrt-linux-uclibc-ld -r -b binary --oformat elf32-tradbigmips -o loader2.o loader.bin
mips-openwrt-linux-uclibc-ld -e startup -T loader2.lds -Ttext 0x80060000 -o loader.elf loader2.o
